# CityPulse — environment variable template
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored) and fill in real values there.
# NEVER put real keys in this file or any other tracked file. `.env*` is gitignored.
#   cp .env.example .env   # then edit .env
#
# The same values live in two places (see NOTES.md):
#   - GitHub Actions secrets  -> used by the nightly pipeline in CI
#   - local .env (gitignored) -> used when you run the pipeline / app on your machine

# --- Google Gemini (runtime + pipeline LLM) ---
# Create/copy at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey  (keep the project on the Free tier)
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# --- Reddit script app (DEFERRED — powers context-brief "chatter"; optional for v1 demo) ---
# Create at https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps  (app type: script)
# REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=
# REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=
# REDDIT_USER_AGENT=citypulse/0.1 by <your-reddit-username>
